{"tid":537574,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"利萊費亞向紅軍挑機：今時唔同往日","createTime":"2018-01-22T22:10:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-23T03:31:37.000Z","uid":2169,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"9f1d1e3a8d36ec55f28081720728e513eb215111","tid":537574,"uid":2169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T22:10:35.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=gt6vtea6%2B%2Bv202uvf3dMSgHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=129e13f2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】史雲斯周一英超主場迎戰利物浦，誓要報仇雪恥，中場主力利萊費亞坦言此一時彼一時，儼如向紅軍下戰書。<br />\n<br />\n首循環，史雲斯作客晏菲路大敗0:5，即使目前仍是英超包尾大幡，但各項賽事近3場保持不敗，信心漸見回升。荷蘭中場利萊費亞（Leroy Fer）認為，新帥卡路士卡華路為球隊注入活力。卡帥接掌的5場比賽，取得2勝2和1負，唯一敗仗是面對熱刺。<br />\n<br />\n利萊費亞表示：「與上次交鋒時不同，己隊進步很大，相信可同紅軍打成均勢。己隊擁有更大信心，希望在主場打敗紅軍。」<br />\n<br />\n紅軍在菲臘比古天奴離隊後，攻擊線仍有穆罕默德沙拿、沙迪奧文尼等猛將，利萊費亞呼籲隊友要打醒十二分精神：「對手是英超最強球隊之一，前線猛將如雲，我們不能輕易失去控球權，紅軍反擊一向凌厲。」史雲斯只有17分在手，落後安全區的17位達6分，情況不容樂觀，必須加倍努力。"},{"pid":"f093a28fe22865102d6dbc9b025922281460d7cb","tid":537574,"uid":2169,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T22:17:02.000Z","msg":"Carlos Carvahal: &ldquo;I told my players: Liverpool is a strong team. Like a Formula 1 car. If you put that F1 car in the 4pm London traffic, the F1 will not drive very fast. That&rsquo;s exactly what we had to do. Let them play in a way they don&rsquo;t like.&rdquo; #lfc"},{"pid":"a2df8e1e9e0018c4a669b958367f2d3b13e2c955","tid":537574,"uid":18385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T22:55:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"021246a61808876d63fdb0a2e3120117b6d55513","tid":537574,"uid":8968,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f093a28fe22865102d6dbc9b025922281460d7cb","tid":537574,"uid":2169,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T22:17:02.000Z","msg":"Carlos Carvahal: &ldquo;I told my players: Liverpool is a strong team. Like a 